rol of plagues<br></li><li>fight against epidemics<br></li><li>deal with natural disasters</li></ul><br>Remember that your king must be satisfied with your work! Do your best to keep the castle alive, the people happy and the army ready for battle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714710/extras/ef30a70ca5beff0e96473c7653cea622.avif?t=1697694364\" width=650 height=101 /></span>",
